definition: adornment/to adorn/dress/clothing/costume (of an actor in a play)/to play a role/to pretend/to install/to fix/to wrap (sth in a bag)/to load/to pack
to enter/to go into/to join/to become a member of/to confirm or agree with/abbr. for 入聲|入声[ru4 sheng1]

sentences.english: Bookmarks have changed on disk and are being reloaded.
sentences.chinese: 已经在磁盘上更改了书签，正在被重新装入。

sentences.english: As this article is fragile, be sure to put enough padding.
sentences.chinese: 此物易碎，请务必装入足够之填充物。

sentences.english: Remove the cover and plunger of the French press.
sentences.chinese: 先将法压壶上方压盖取出，将咖啡粉装入壶中。

sentences.english: The multi-language Babylon dictionary has been inserted on the translation pages at the bottom of the side menu.
sentences.chinese: 网页底部的菜单已经装入多语种巴比伦字典。

sentences.english: Library loading and unloading introduces some issues, such as the need to take care of static objects.
sentences.chinese: 库装入和卸装引入一些问题，如需要注意静态对象。

sentences.english: If you only put the best possible ingredients into that machine body, it will work flawlessly.
sentences.chinese: 如果你将最好的部件装入这台机器，它将完美的运作。

sentences.english: He was shot by a misloaded prop gun.
sentences.chinese: 他被装入真子弹的道具手枪打死。

sentences.english: The soldiers charged their guns and prepared to fire.
sentences.chinese: 兵士们将子弹装入枪膛准备射击。

sentences.english: Follow these steps to download, unzip and install to TRAINZ .
sentences.chinese: 按下列步骤下载，解压缩后完整装入TRAINZ。

sentences.english: A woman sorts garlic to be filled in sacks in a shed.
sentences.chinese: 在一个工棚里，一位妇女筛选大蒜并装入麻袋里。

sentences.english: The cargo was containerized for safe and efficient shipping.
sentences.chinese: 为了安全有效率的运输，货物被装入集装箱内。

sentences.english: This error is thrown during the initialization phase of class loading.
sentences.chinese: 这个错误在类装入的初始化阶段抛出。

sentences.english: To lessen the resonance from the HDD I used rubber rings to mount it in place.
sentences.chinese: 为了减少从硬盘我用橡胶圈装入到位的共鸣。

sentences.english: This refactoring will ask you to provide a name for the enclosing instance.
sentences.chinese: 这种重构要求您为装入实例提供一个名字。

sentences.english: Then use the following subroutine to load the field weights into memory.
sentences.chinese: 然后使用以下子例程将字段权重装入内存。
